data.description: Under Construction. Brand NEW energy-efficient home ready December 2020! Entertain with ease in the Marigold's spacious kitchen with adjoining dining and great room. Kitchen cabinets with quartz countertops and grey floor tile. Upstairs loft can be used to best fit your family's needs. Covered patio in the back of home. Lucerne Park Reserve is located in historic Winter Haven only one mile from US-27 providing easy access to major employment centers. This charming community is close to town centers with plenty of restaurant and retail options. Known for their energy-efficient features, our homes help you live a healthier and quieter lifestyle while saving thousands of dollars on utility bills.
